These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Transport      | quad-bike  | snowmobile | scooter        | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, chinese, canadian
1. the canadian is somewhere between the chinese and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the canadian is between the chinese and the mexican##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Nationality   | mexican   | canadian | chinese | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, ritmeester, montecristo, prince
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, house, indie
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##7
3. the fan of house is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of indie and the ritmeester-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | prince | montecristo | bolivar  |
| Music-Genre   | house | classical  | indie   | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, white, amber, fuchsia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person who likes fuchsia##7
3. the person who likes amber is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | white | lavender | fuchsia       | amber |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

