.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
City: san-francisco, hannover, prague, edinburgh
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to san-francisco##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City         | prague | san-francisco   | edinburgh | hannover |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

