4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, ritmeester, bluemaster
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
6. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere between the bongani-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##7
7. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Cigar   | bongani    | bluemaster | alhambra   | ritmeester |

