.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rugby, golf, baseball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Sport   | soccer | golf | baseball    | rugby |

