.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, water, fanta
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the person drinking lemonade is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking soy-milk##7
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | water | lemonade | soy-milk |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

