2. the person watching satire movies is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Sport           | badminton    | snowboarding   | basketball  | soccer      |

