2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person watching documentary movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation | documentary | epic   |
| Hobby   | collecting    | chess      | reading      | gardening |

