4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person driving the car is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Transport      | trike   | subway | car | snowmobile   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | house   | indie | hip-hop |

