2. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who growsbegonia##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growspoppy##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku     | drawing     | rock-climbing |
| Flower     | begonia | poppy | tulip | iris     |

