.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
House: modern, craftsman, townhouse, colonial
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the modern house and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the modern house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| House   | townhouse | colonial  | craftsman | modern |

 